{"tid":1947721,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"約翰遜有身孕 弟婦確診武肺","createTime":"2020-03-28T12:59:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-28T20:31:43.000Z","uid":80775,"like":38,"dislike":132,"uniUserReply":59,"replies":[{"pid":"bc2c4abec173880dd80244144fe4b1cb73e158a0","tid":1947721,"uid":80775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T12:59:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/WVhPq_Rqh3ugpiQ7UHlrM9xwfY8=/802x451/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/ZB3WDCW544G5XW5XAPMCIRMMA4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FWVhPq_Rqh3ugpiQ7UHlrM9xwfY8%3D%2F802x451%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FZB3WDCW544G5XW5XAPMCIRMMA4.jpg&h=33a60ba6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n約翰遜弟婦、30歲的邁亞（Gabriela Maia）周五晚上表示確診武漢肺炎，「目前正慢慢康復，仍有少許呼吸困難」，「我現在安好，仍能生存感到很幸運，我祈求寶寶也安全。我為那些不那麼幸運的人感到心痛，非常、非常悲傷。」<br />\n<br />\n英國超過有1.45萬宗確診感染病例，至少759人死亡，除了長者和患有長期病患的人士之外，孕婦也是高危的染疫群組。而約翰遜的未婚妻西蒙斯（Carrie Symonds）也正懷胎五月，預計孩子在初夏出生。英國《太陽報》報道，西蒙斯「數日前」離開唐寧街11號，獨自於他們位於坎伯韋爾(Camberwell)的大宅中居住。今年3月，約翰遜在與前妻離婚後不足兩周，宣佈與西蒙斯奉子訂婚。"},{"pid":"e3ac6de93e27770bf0959c93f1350efe67a22177","tid":1947721,"uid":196924,"like":70,"dislike":4,"score":66,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T13:00:36.000Z","msg":"佢弟婦冇冠夫姓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be6d27a998bc0a81888a1095a25d1c59fc16d68a","tid":1947721,"uid":196924,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T13:01:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">Carrie</span> Symonds"},{"pid":"85b0552f5b43982d4b17839562a10d5ffb162285","tid":1947721,"uid":5649,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"e3ac6de93e27770bf0959c93f1350efe67a22177","tid":1947721,"uid":196924,"like":70,"dislike":4,"score":66,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T13:00:36.000Z","msg":"佢弟婦冇冠夫姓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\