rong>。<br />\n睇返佢個底，完全係20世紀初英國間諜嗰種人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：<br />\n&mdash;清華畢業生<br />\n&mdash;流利中文、俄文<br />\n&mdash;前任中國英國商會副主席<br />\n&mdash;大陸英國文化協會嗰舊Generation UK: China Network嘅顧問<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><br />\n[呢個人相當有可疑]英國真會幫我地？睇下新首相住喺香港個細佬嘅底細！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1363189\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1363189</a></span><br />\n<br />\nHe <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">expects to become a Hong Kong permanent resident early next year after living here for seven years</span></strong></strong></span>, most of which was spent working for a British metals trading house and investment bank Goldman Sachs.<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"https://www.scmp.com/business/banking-finance/article/3022223/boris-johnsons-brother-hong-kong-backs-his-brexit-strategy\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmp.com%2Fbusiness%2Fbanking-finance%2Farticle%2F3022223%2Fboris-johnsons-brother-hong-kong-backs-his-brexit-strategy&d=g1YLBr7c5t2fgTVFseaOq0YZmLIq74JPLN0FyuDKESI%3D&h=d365cff6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.scmp.com/business/banking-finance/article/3022223/boris-johnsons-brother-hong-kong-backs-his-brexit-strategy</a></span>"},{"pid":"b33e5d76cd65908daf2aa38a0b30439339546da8","tid":1947721,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ad194945f18a339bc9e3e63a731928ceb3177a42","tid":1947721,"uid":50196,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-28T14:41:13.000Z","msg":"呢個<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">Max Johnson</span></span></strong>係Boris Johnson嘅細佬（同父異母，但超似樣）<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">而家係香港從事金融業</span></strong>。<br />\n睇返佢個底，完全係20世紀初英國間諜嗰種人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：<br />\n&mdash;清華畢業生<br />\n&mdash;流利中文、俄文<br />\n&mdash;前任中國英國商會副主席<br />\n&m